{"tid":1960513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葵盛東邨六條廢老聚集未理警勸喻獲發告票","createTime":"2020-04-06T08:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T08:12:38.000Z","uid":62350,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f528d9907c4a8aeb1004a437da8f0722045f274f","tid":1960513,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:11:05.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府宣布禁止多於四人在公眾地方聚集規例生效多於一星期，據了解，警方星期日首次發出定額罰款告票。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，星期日葵青警區接獲報案，指在葵盛東邨有人聚集。警方到場發現，有六名男子正在下棋，他們未有理會警方勸喻，保持適當距離或離開，警方於是向六人發出告票。<br />\n<br />\n上月29日凌晨起，在公眾地方多於4人的群組聚集均屬犯罪，違者須繳付定額罰款2000元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fc7dc2461cc1484f6a3db2718b0019af756d58","tid":1960513,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"萬二蚊！"},{"pid":"977a53f1f44847d6b17e5656360fb97e2858af13","tid":1960513,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:12:38.000Z","msg":"捉棋都攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}